              <span id="reviewTextContainer2292885293" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17963745650904808477">Two young cops pull over two thieving sociopaths, and the murder of one shatters lives for decades to come. <br/><br/>This is a classic -- a must-read for true crime geeks. The only buzz kill for me was in the dragging pace that consumes several areas of the book. <br/><br/>A solid 4 stars out of 5.</span>

          </span>
